title: Skip SSH Host Verification in Ansible
tags: @zettel _method ansible ssh
roam-id: eddda427-aebc-48dd-983b-dcee452c1890
type: text/markdown

add this to your script or shell before running ansible

``` shell
export ANSIBLE_HOST_KEY_CHECKING=False
```

or put this into `ansible.cfg`

``` toml
[defaults]
host_key_checking = False
inventory = ./inventory/jenkins.ini
roles_path = ./roles
```
